  • Description: THE LEAKING PACKAGE WAS FOUND AT THE PD4 LOW VOLUME PICKOFF AT APPROXIMATELY 17:32 ON 12/17/24. IT WAS DISCOVERED THAT THE BOX CONTAINED TWO SUSPECTED UNDECLARED HAZMATS: THE LEAKING MERCHANDISE "MG CHEMICALS 824 ISOPROPYL ALCOHOL ELECTRONICS CLEANER," AND AN AEROSOL "MUC-OFF BIKE PROTECT." THE SUSPECTED UNDECLARED HAZMAT WAS REPORTED TO RMP. PACKAGE HELD FOR VALIDATION.
